Value: The GO2 People Limited provides recruitment and training services in Australia. Its Recruitment division offers staffing solutions for various sectors, including infrastructure, construction, mining/resources, electrical/energy, waste management, and warehousing/logistics. The company also provides training and education service to its clients, which includes accredited and non-accredited workplace training and education courses; and a suite of blue-collar employment services, including pre-employment programs, traineeships and apprenticeships, and fee-for-service recruitment and labor hire services. The GO2 People Limited was founded in 2011 and is based in Forrestfield, Australia.
